14.title: 107 Hotel Transylvania Facts YOU Should Know!
14.plot: There's only one place where the spookiest monsters come to have a good time, and it's "Hotel Transylvania". ToonedUp has 107 Facts on the hilarious animated film about Dracula and his gang of ghouls who are trying to keep their hotel a secret from nosy humans. You'll learn all sorts of crazy hidden gems you never noticed were in the film, as well as insane facts about the movie's insanely lengthy production. So get all your werewolf pups together and prepare to party with some monsters because ToonedUp has 107 facts about "Hotel Transylvania".

15.title: 107 Over the Garden Wall Facts YOU Should Know!
15.plot: The world of the Unknown is beautiful - but it can also be dangerous if you don't know the way; that's why ToonedUp is helping you out with 107 facts you should know about "Over The Garden Wall". The incredible miniseries follows brothers Wirt and Greg as they attempt to find their way through a strange forest with the help of some peculiar characters. There's so many hidden secrets in each episode that you probably never even noticed them. So make sure you hug your frog pal tight because ToonedUp is taking you "Over The Garden Wall" with 107 facts.

16.title: 107 the Lion King Facts YOU Should Know!
16.plot: There's but one animated film that people from all generations can agree is one of the most imaginative and visually stunning pieces of cartoon history: "The Lion King". The legendary flick is one of Disney's most popular animated films ever, and ToonedUp is giving you 107 facts you should know about it. You won't believe all of the crazy stories behind the catchy music and mind-blowing art that helped make it an unforgettable classic. So get ready because ToonedUp is giving you 107 slimy yet satisfying facts you should know about "The Lion King".

17.title: 107 Hey Arnold Facts YOU Should Know!
17.plot: Who would've thought that a show about kid with "football head" would be one the most cherished cartoons of the '90s. "Hey Arnold" follows the story of Arnold and his friends' hilarious misadventures living in the big city. But you probably didn't know about all the secret facts behind the legendary cartoon's production, from canceled movies to different endings to classic episodes. So join ToonedUp as we proudly give you 107 "Hey Arnold" facts you should know.

18.title: 107 Rugrats Facts YOU Should Know!
18.plot: When you were just a kid and the world seemed like one big adventure, you could always count on the "Rugrats" to guide you. The classic Nickelodeon cartoon followed the antics of Tommy, Chuckie, Phil and Lil, and Angelica (sometimes Susie) as they navigated through the hilarious world of adults. We all loved watching the kids sneak away and exploring the world as it appeared to their imaginative minds; but as a kid, you probably never stopped to analyze the show for it's facts and production secrets. Well get ready to roar like the mighty Reptar because ToonedUp's got...

19.title: 107 DuckTales Facts YOU Should Know!
19.plot: Some would say that Disney was making their best cartoons during the '90s, most notably with the jet-setting adventures of "DuckTales". Scrooge McDuck and his great-nephews Huey, Dewey, and Louie had all sorts of awesome adventures that rivaled that of Indiana Jones and even the most action-packed cartoons today. But as a kid, you probably had no idea of how much thought went into developing the show and making it as much Disney fun as possible. This week, life will resemble that of a hurricane as ToonedUp gives you 107 facts you should know about "DuckTales".

20.title: 107 Facts About Nightmare Before Christmas!
20.plot: If there's a movie that blends the spooky fun of Halloween and the cheerful spirit of Christmas, it has to be the claymation cult classic "The Nightmare Before Christmas". The story of Jack the Pumpkin King trying to spread Christmas cheer in his world of Halloween Town has been a favorite holiday film for years, but there's much more lurking beneath the film's delightful creepy surface than you may know. So prepare to be scared stiff as ToonedUp gives you 107 "Nightmare Before Christmas" facts you should know.

21.title: 107 Channel Frederator Facts YOU Should Know!
21.plot: Channel Frederator has been home to the best and newest cartoons on the internet for over a decade. And having just turned 10 years old, we've decided to flip the ToonedUp lens on ourselves to give you 107 facts about Channel Frederator. From our small beginnings, to becoming the biggest network of animators on the internet, we have plenty of awesome milestones to cover. So get ready for things to get super meta, because ToonedUp has 107 facts about Channel Frederator.

22.title: 107 Facts About the Peanuts!
22.plot: "Peanuts" is a truly legendary cartoon that's known the world over for it's humor and charm. It's one of the best comic strips of all time, home to some of the best holiday specials ever and is finally a 3D movie for new generations of kids to enjoy. And ever since it's creation in the 1950's, it's obviously accumulated some pretty interesting facts and stories. In honor of Charles Schulz and the newest film being released worldwide, ToonedUp is proud to present 107 facts about "Peanuts".

23.title: 107 Facts About Beauty and the Beast!
23.plot: Very few animated films have been as critically acclaimed as Disney's "Beauty and the Beast." The film symbolized a new era of brilliant Disney films and even broke records for being the first animated film to be nominated for "Best Picture" at the Academy Awards. But how much do you really know about the timeless love story and all of the crazy behind the scenes magic that made it great? That's why this week on ToonedUp we want you to be our guest as we proudly present 107 Facts about "Beauty and The Beast."

24.title: 107 Facts About the Good Dinosaur!
24.plot: What would it have been like if dinosaurs HADN'T gone extinct 65 million years ago; the answer is Pixar's next great film "The Good Dinosaur" The animated movie follows Arlo, a talking dinosaur who comes across a young feral boy, Spot, who joins him on his quest to find his missing dino family. A lot about the film and it's production have been kept under wraps, but ToonedUp has done it's research and is giving you 107 facts about Pixar's "The Good Dinosaur".

25.title: 107 MORE Facts About the Simpsons!
25.plot: For one of the longest running shows in television history (cartoon or otherwise), there's plenty of information about "The Simpsons" that we only scratched the surface of in our last 107 Facts. That's why we're going back to the big yellow well to see what other crazy info we can find the second time around. From last minute decisions that could have changed characters forever to behind-the-scenes events that could've affected the show's history, we've got a lot of juicy facts for all you fans to enjoy. So crack a Duff and make yourself comfy because ToonedUp has ...

1.title: 107 MORE Facts About Gravity Falls!
1.plot: It's one of the most mysterious cartoon shows on television to date, so of course a mere 107 facts wasn't enough to satisfy our curiosity of "Gravity Falls". The series is sadly coming to an end but that doesn't mean we can't analyze the heck out of this delightfully weird program. We have even more Easter eggs to dissect and clues to study to better help us understand the many mysteries that surround The Pines family. So get ready for some serious weirdness because ToonedUp has 107 MORE facts about "Gravity Falls".

2.title: 107 Facts About Kung Fu Panda!
2.plot: No bear that can kick as much butt as Po from Dreamwork's cartoon karate films, "Kung Fu Panda" and it's clear to see why. Po's journey of trying to become a kung-fu master have made the series easily one of the most beautiful/epic CG-animated films of all time. From the intense attention to detail in the fighting, to the voice actors' passion for their roles make the series an incredibly unique experience. That's why ToonedUp is proud to hype you up with 107 facts about the "Kung Fu Panda" movies.

3.title: 107 Facts About Frosty the Snowman!
3.plot: We all know the song and/or Holiday special of the magical snowman who came to life and became "Frosty the Snowman". The holiday special has been warming hearts since the '60s and has become basically a symbol for winter fun times. But there's probably a great deal you don't know about how the story came to be and the unusual circumstances that led it to being such a cherished special. That's why ToonedUp is getting into the spirit of the holiday and giving you 107 facts about "Frosty The Snowman".
